      • mouseClicked

        public void mouseClicked​(java.awt.event.MouseEvent e)
        For Calculate and Reset Buttons. If event came from the Calculate button, it will run errorCheckGenes() to verify all selected genes are assigned a symbol and selected alleles from both parents. Reset button will clear all symbol JComboBoxes and ButtonGroups to default.
        Specified by:
        mouseClicked in interface java.awt.event.MouseListener

      • itemStateChanged

        public void itemStateChanged​(java.awt.event.ItemEvent e)
        Activates when a user changes the selected item in a JComboBox. Depending on the Gene Row it's on, it will enable the JComboBox of the Gene Row below it. Additionally, it will activate the current row's ButtonGroups to select a corresponding allele type.
        Specified by:
        itemStateChanged in interface java.awt.event.ItemListener
        Parameters:
        e - ItemEvent

      • toggleButtonGroup

        private void toggleButtonGroup​(javax.swing.ButtonGroup buttonGroup)
        Acts as a toggle switch for ButtonGroups. Takes in a JRadioButton ButtonGroup, cycles through the list and if they are enabled with ItemListeners, disable them. Otherwise enable them.
        Parameters:
        buttonGroup - ButtonGroup

      • toggleNextComboBox

        private void toggleNextComboBox​(javax.swing.JComboBox<java.lang.String> comboBox)
        Acts like a switch to toggle the JComboBox enabled or disabled. If enabled with ItemListeners remove them, disable the JComboBox, and set the selected item in the list to the first item(default item)
        Parameters:
        comboBox - JComboBox

      • updateParentTwoComboBox

        private void updateParentTwoComboBox​(javax.swing.JComboBox<java.lang.String> comboBox,
                                     int indexPos)
        To update ParentTwo's disabled JComboBox. Takes in a JComboBox, and an int value related to an index position in the JComboBox. It enables the JComboBox, sets the selected index to the corresponding index number passed, and disables the JComboBox again.
        Parameters:
        comboBox - JComboBox
        indexPos - integer

      • updateButtonGroup

        private void updateButtonGroup​(java.lang.String labelText,
                               javax.swing.ButtonGroup buttonGroup)
        Updates each JRadioButton's Label text in the ButtonGroup given. The newText parameter must be capitalized. If this method was called in lieu of deactivating its ButtonGroup, it will turn the label texts into A equivalents.
        Parameters:
        labelText - String
        buttonGroup - ButtonGroup

      • resetAll

        private void resetAll()
        Resets the first JComboBox to default, which cascades through all five potentially active JComboBoxes to reset them. Also resets the JTextArea where results are shown.

      • errorCheckGenes

        private boolean errorCheckGenes()
        Checks to see which Gene Rows are enabled. If enabled, verify they have a selected symbol, and in each parent's ButtonGroup has a selected JRadioButton(allele). Otherwise it will add to the error message, and set the boolean to flag to false. If the boolean was flagged, it'll call a error pop-up message to display which lines have errors.
        Returns:
        noErrors boolean

      • hasButtonSelected

        private boolean hasButtonSelected​(javax.swing.ButtonGroup buttonGroup)
        This method checks to see if one of the ButtonGroup's JRadioButtons are selected. If it finds one, it returns true, otherwise it returns false.
        Parameters:
        buttonGroup - ButtonGroup
        Returns:
        isButtonSelected boolean

      • startCalculation

        private void startCalculation()
        Builds the Genes by checking all five relevant JComboBoxes. Then gets the boolean value from each of the corresponding buttons in Parent One and Parent Two's ButtonGroups. Two parent objects are built with the Genes, and sent to build the punnett square. Finally, after built it displays the results.

        Parameters:
        results - List
